程序包 org.elasticsearch.join.mapper

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    MetaJoinFieldMapper
    Simple field mapper hack to ensure that there is a one and only ParentJoinFieldMapper per mapping.
    MetaJoinFieldMapper.MetaJoinFieldType  
    ParentIdFieldMapper
    A field mapper used internally by the ParentJoinFieldMapper to index the value that link documents in the index (parent _id or _id if the document is a parent).
    ParentIdFieldMapper.ParentIdFieldType  
    ParentJoinFieldMapper
    A FieldMapper that creates hierarchical joins (parent-join) between documents in the same index.
    ParentJoinFieldMapper.Builder  
    ParentJoinFieldMapper.Defaults  
    ParentJoinFieldMapper.JoinFieldType  
    ParentJoinFieldMapper.TypeParser
